data.description: Welcome home to 2726 Ember Pass Lane Located in The Desirable Cinco Ranch NW neighborhood and zoned to A+ Rated schools in Katy ISD! This Smart Home has many features that can be controlled from your phone. This Stunning home features 5 bedrooms, 3 full baths 2 car garage. As you open the front door to this open floor plan you are welcomed by the Rotunda with Coffered Ceilings. Entertain your guest in the formal dining that shares a Cast Iron Stone Double sided fireplace with the Family Room featuring built in surround sound . Primary bath includes separate sinks, Jacuzzi tub, separate walk-in  shower with 2 walk-in closets. In the back you will find double doors leading to the covered patio with gas line for the Grill.  Schedule your showing today!!
